{"tid":1910960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"貿易協議恐難履行 美國財政委員會主席格拉斯利：美國需留點餘地給中國","createTime":"2020-03-05T04:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T05:24:03.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9bfb0ca76e58ac7f204d2382c24b05118993f498","tid":1910960,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2020/03/05/php112oCK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2020%2F03%2F05%2Fphp112oCK.jpg&h=e614d46a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n財政委員會主席、共和黨參議員格拉斯利。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美國、中國1月15日簽署的第1階段貿易協議已於2月生效，然而武漢肺炎疫情衝擊各行業與經濟，各界更加懷疑中國能否履約。美國財政委員會主席、共和黨參議員格拉斯利（Chuck Grassley）週三則表示，美國需要給中國「留點餘地」。<br />\n<br />\n格拉斯利受《路透》採訪表示，他沒看到中國逃避承諾的意圖。像是降低部份美國商品的進口關稅，或是放寬美國食品添加物的標準等等，都表明他們有誠意履約。<br />\n<br />\n但格拉斯利稱，新型冠狀病毒爆發後中國經濟重挫，情況可能需要做些調整，且第2階段貿易協議談判應該也會順延。「由於中國的經濟低迷、導致消費量減低，因此我們必須給他們一些餘地。」<br />\n<br />\n格拉斯利補充，聯準會降息可能有助於抵銷病毒的負面影響，但是降低對中關稅將是美國政府在必要時刻刺激經濟的方式，會比國會通過減稅方案還快得多。<br />\n<br />\n在疫情爆發之前，專家們就提出中國市場需求或購買力恐怕不足以履行協議，按約中國到2020年底須增加購買770億美元的美國商品。1位駐華盛頓的中國官員上週表示，中方認真執行該協議，但航空停滯、旅行禁令等將使實現這些目標複雜化。<br />\n<br />\n美國農業部長帕度（Sonny Perdue）週三則說，預計中國會在春末與夏季重新採購美國大豆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3089095\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3089095&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIH4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=3b5d3722\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3089095&h=c213aa47\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3089095</a>"},{"pid":"0eaaf4e4a15f045f0ff5430e7f8be45f074cbca0","tid":1910960,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:32:06.000Z","msg":"中國又成最大贏家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202002/2e8990012ac165fc29fc162ec3d83b5a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202002%2F2e8990012ac165fc29fc162ec3d83b5a.JPG&h=47ec7804&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9502058c6b90ff043ef520ba1775706dd31fed4b","tid":1910960,"uid":249979,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:32:09.000Z","msg":"對敵人仁慈即係對自己殘忍<br />\n呢條傻鳩仲信支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338f821ff90549acac0eecba2297aa10884cf5e1","tid":1910960,"uid":167548,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9502058c6b90ff043ef520ba1775706dd31fed4b","tid":1910960,"uid":249979,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:32:09.000Z","msg":"對敵人仁慈即係對自己殘忍<br />\n呢條傻鳩仲信支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:32:42.000Z","msg":"姑息養奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a980d1b124f6c11c6b8132c12089c0391633c936","tid":1910960,"uid":137725,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:33:11.000Z","msg":"仍然係左膠當道<br />\n受道德觀念束縛覺得凡事留一線"},{"pid":"42a5412d25dd522ffa48da7f48c9f3fa043dc7ce","tid":1910960,"uid":8410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:33:22.000Z","msg":"呢個時候仲大愛？ 定奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4fc345dbd51eceb55ed68184eaf77953a26f5c","tid":1910960,"uid":